All 33 tests still pass. The fixes applied from the review:

- **Position guard fix (HIGH)**: now divides by non-empty line count (`lines.filter(l => l.trim().length > 0).length`) instead of raw `lines.length`, making the 75% threshold consistent across documents with varying blank-line density.
- **Edge case comment (MEDIUM)**: documented that the `else` fallback in the guard is a known no-op when all candidates are in the last 25%.
- **`ciasto` comment (MEDIUM)**: clarified it's intentionally in the recipe-section group (dough/pastry base) and also covers the chapter-label meaning.
